{"tid":2061114,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"BNO簽發 去年飆至13萬本","createTime":"2020-06-12T07:08:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T13:02:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f6315a66045ed74a8afa222118cd0f6ff099eb29","tid":2061114,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T07:08:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200612/ITHBIR5LAMCKA56QSNWV7TFWGA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200612%2FITHBIR5LAMCKA56QSNWV7TFWGA%2F&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjFtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=ea9149ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200612%2FITHBIR5LAMCKA56QSNWV7TFWGA%2F&h=996826ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200612/ITHBIR5LAMCKA56QSNWV7TFWGA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\nBNO簽發 去年飆至13萬本<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KBZJGONLTXWLXYWZL4Q45ZU5B4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKBZJGONLTXWLXYWZL4Q45ZU5B4.jpg&h=73d6f2c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSamson一直在民間爭取BNO平權，但對英國政府偏軟態度不予厚望。<br />\n<br />\n由反修例運動開始，BNO就被視為港人的「逃生門」，去年簽發的BNO數目更突破10萬大關，勢創近八年新高。英國政府早前表示，若香港落實港版國安法，擬向290萬BNO持有人給予居留權，並研究將BNO 免簽證入境期限由6個月延至一年，再給港人曙光。有爭取BNO平權的人士認為，計劃現階段欠詳情，料會視乎中方反應再決定是否兌現承諾。即使成事，若逗留條件不變，亦難吸引港人赴英。<br />\n<br />\n逾半年的反修例風波激發港人續領BNO意欲，英國內政部護照署數字顯示，截至去年上半年的BNO簽。。。。。。。。。。。。。。量突破十萬大關，多達131,102本，較過去七年的全年平均數約22,000本多出3.7倍，勢成八年新高。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RAXUVBHUIAKZ7DWQSAAVU5VMEE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRAXUVBHUIAKZ7DWQSAAVU5VMEE.gif&h=d2e668b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/H7AYJQF6OV4FJLMND7BIRWHCP4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FH7AYJQF6OV4FJLMND7BIRWHCP4.gif&h=1bfa2111&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LAHCMYLVSDSGJKNXLG3JUV6FTY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLAHCMYLVSDSGJKNXLG3JUV6FTY.gif&h=54b54171&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n平權實質方案欠奉<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：國安法嚇走年輕專業人士<br />\n<br />\n「英國國民海外護照平權運動」組織多年來敦促英國給予BNO持。<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。。請教續領步驟，「唔使叫都自動波啦，香港人有着數點會唔爭崩頭呀？」<br />\n<br />\nSamson口中的着數，是英國外相藍韜文上月底建議向持有人提供的居英權。BNO平權。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。nal（警示）。」他更擔心，若中央突然決定不推港版國安法，英方承諾隨時變泡影。<br />\n<br />\n目前約30萬人持有有效BNO，而在1997年回歸中。。。。。。。。。。。。英權的說法僅流於「吹水」，完全未見有實際程序。<br />\n<br />\n在此前提下，續領BNO暫未有助移民。即使日後有收留港人方案出台，Samson估計礙於資金及其他逗留條件。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。夠金錢到當地生活。他料在有關條件下，BNO持。。。。。。。。。,000人。"},{"pid":"8171f7fe24670ee1e5c5b9e224437ef743d0ec0a","tid":2061114,"uid":254788,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T07:22:39.000Z","msg":"根本都係嗰句<br />\n英國有心就97年好似澳門咁派左護照啦"},{"pid":"3c1194dfaddc87a002b2a746f65b11fc527ccdd1","tid":2061114,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T07:23:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1acbae87d56fb4c20be874e65f9162999f6da84","tid":2061114,"uid":58387,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8171f7fe24670ee1e5c5b9e224437ef743d0ec0a","tid":2061114,"uid":254788,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T07:22:39.000Z","msg":"根本都係嗰句<br />\n英國有心就97年好似澳門咁派左護照啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T07:38:05.000Z","msg":"當年中英聯合聲明傾左唔比派護照比香港人<br />\n要香港人世世代代做芝麻人<br />\n相反澳門就比［最終，中方容許葡裔澳門人自行選擇國籍（即中國籍或維持葡萄牙國籍）］"},{"pid":"5ac0ada35d7598c9a7d71b0cba8256bb57a3ed6d","tid":2061114,"uid":3383,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T07:49:22.000Z","msg":"蘋果日報啲用字真係幾嬲屌，<br />\n<br />\nHome office 唔係出咗fact sheet 架咩，真係唔撚知你班友係唔係呃飯食。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://homeofficemedia.blog.gov.uk/2020/05/29/media-factsheet-hong-kong-bnos/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhomeofficemedia.blog.gov.uk%2F2020%2F05%2F29%2Fmedia-factsheet-hong-kong-bnos%2F&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjFtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=f3636045\" target=\"_blank\">https://homeofficemedia.blog.gov.uk/2020/05/29/media-factsheet-hong-kong-bnos/</a><br />\n<br />\n1. 香港主權移交前有344萬人持有BN(O)「地位」<br />\n2. 根據1985年香港法案，BN(O)「身份」為新設立嘅「英國國籍」。<br />\n3. 根據1986年香港(英國國籍)令，BN(O)「地位」於1987年7月1日正式接受申請。<br />\n4. 有資格登記成為BN(O)「地位」人士必須為香港英國屬土公民「地位」(BDTC)<br />\n5. 1997年1月1日至6月30日出生嘅人登記期限為1997年9月30日前，其餘人士嘅期限為同年6月30日。<br />\n6. 任何人都無法於上述限期之後登記成為BN(O)。<br />\n7. 登記手續完成後將獲發一本國籍欄印上British National (Overseas)嘅英國護照(下稱BN(O)「護照」)<br />\n8. BN(O)「地位」係終身持有，BN(O)「護照」只係用黎證明你持有呢個「地位」，「地位」不會隨「護照」而過期而消失，當「護照」已經遺失、被盜、破損、用滿或過期時，可以隨時續領新嘅BN(O)「護照」。<br />\n<br />\n所以，截至2020年2月24日，總持有BN(O)「地位」人數為約290萬，當中有349881人持有有效BN(O)「護照」，其餘人士該BN(O)「護照」已經過期。<br />\n<br />\n講到「目前約30萬人持有有效BNO，而在1997年回歸中國，此前出生的290萬香港公民都有資格申請BNO」咁嘅款，我唔知係我閱讀理解唔好定係佢中文有問題啦。"},{"pid":"af8cb450b7b8b54b5e96b854eb1eca3d1f9bd2f6","tid":2061114,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T07:55:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2019年數字</span></span><br />\n<br />\n直至2019年12月31日為止，續領護照數字為：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">154,218</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EzgCbeF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEzgCbeF.png&h=52e61e5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到2019年12月31日為止，有效護照數字為：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">314,779</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mpn54zE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMpn54zE.png&h=9922b820&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.whatdotheyknow.com/request/634155/response/1523562/attach/2/FOICR%2057241%20Luke%20Lo%20final%20response.pdf?cookie_passthrough=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatdotheyknow.com%2Frequest%2F634155%2Fresponse%2F1523562%2Fattach%2F2%2FFOICR%252057241%2520Luke%2520Lo%2520final%2520response.pdf%3Fcookie_passthrough%3D1&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjFtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=46ff1a34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.whatdotheyknow.com/request/634155/response/1523562/attach/2/FOICR%2057241%20Luke%20Lo%20final%20response.pdf?cookie_passthrough=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到2020年3月19日為止，有效護照數字為：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">349,881</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nAs of February ​2020, there were 349,881 British national (overseas) passport holders in Hong Kong, out of an estimated 2.9 million people eligible for such status.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hansard.parliament.uk/Lords/2020-03-19/debates/3E240399-C146-44F1-B1B6-315C79026BBD/HongKongCovid-19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhansard.parliament.uk%2FLords%2F2020-03-19%2Fdebates%2F3E240399-C146-44F1-B1B6-315C79026BBD%2FHongKongCovid-19&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjFtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=c472b62d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hansard.parliament.uk/Lords/2020-03-19/debates/3E240399-C146-44F1-B1B6-315C79026BBD/HongKongCovid-19</a>"},{"pid":"ad96efdd9958b34876da2718b749757d2112edbd","tid":2061114,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T07:55:38.000Z","msg":"一年簽13萬本但總數有效得30萬本？"},{"pid":"4821aa62cbe0dacc9489732bf3f02a1040217d98","tid":2061114,"uid":3383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad96efdd9958b34876da2718b749757d2112edbd","tid":2061114,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T07:55:38.000Z","msg":"一年簽13萬本但總數有效得30萬本？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20